{"id": 622, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么样的夸赞让你觉得夸张又暗爽？", "description": "全宇宙的情商都长这个人身上了吧！", "record_count": 7430, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183645pNEHf45cLm793OG8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-06T11:04:50Z", "options": [{"id": 22786, "content": "要不是看你聪明还挺美 我早打你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119305}, {"id": 23554, "content": "要是你也算胖，全世界没瘦子了好嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292934}, {"id": 23043, "content": "你这个东西哪里抠的？～啊，我自己画的啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289636}, {"id": 24323, "content": "要不是因为你长得好看谁想跟你做朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299550}, {"id": 28420, "content": "你长得那么好帅，晚上我都愿意让你送我回家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324327}, {"id": 22789, "content": "哟，你什么时候会xxx的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216032}, {"id": 22791, "content": "你这么漂亮你还担心个毛啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280927}, {"id": 25607, "content": "。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305268}, {"id": 22793, "content": "11111", "image": "img/option/option/201607021824512P5fWVURldIzq1jS.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194236}, {"id": 22795, "content": "你长得这么好看，做的菜怎么这么难吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 22796, "content": "你学语言的天分真的好高哎～", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270532}, {"id": 23052, "content": "看到就点赞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290272}, {"id": 22797, "content": "别蒙我，你没有男/女朋友我吃翔！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282203}, {"id": 23053, "content": "你是不是偷偷用你妈的护肤品了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 24077, "content": "不要仗着自己略有姿色就任性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290672}, {"id": 22798, "content": "和你在一起很舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287315}, {"id": 23054, "content": "叫我绿茶婊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 194574, "content": "要不是看你长得那么好看，谁会天天担心你的安全呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009914}, {"id": 22799, "content": "“你的鼻子挺的好像外国人啊！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187946}, {"id": 23567, "content": "你是不是大学整容了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292949}, {"id": 22801, "content": "你胸大还嫌我手小", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282203}, {"id": 23314, "content": "被瞎了的人夸长得好看 被逗比夸情商高 被聋了的人夸唱歌好听 [被夸心情就超棒的耶!!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291740}, {"id": 22805, "content": "我很少看到这样双商都高的人……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259431}, {"id": 22806, "content": "你的品味真不错啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287249}, {"id": 22810, "content": "胸大了不起啊！胸大腰细了不起啊！！( ﹁ ﹁ ) ~→", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245341}, {"id": 22812, "content": "No one deserve you.", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288818}, {"id": 23324, "content": "我儿子七岁 哇 你看起来好年轻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201244}, {"id": 29980, "content": "人长得帅，穿啥都好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331744}, {"id": 22813, "content": "我知道你“才大器粗！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288866}, {"id": 42271, "content": "你好帅啊，我好爱你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429564}, {"id": 22816, "content": "啊～没那么舒服过", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255821}, {"id": 22817, "content": "你又变帅了。??", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215053}, {"id": 22822, "content": "“长得像吴彦祖，就可以先干嘛干嘛？！”", "image": "img/option/option/201606052118077Tvl5ADcsgaJnE6M.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 22823, "content": "“不要以为你长得跟天仙似的，我就不生气了！”", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211736qBEZ2VwxK0TSNUtX.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 22824, "content": "小姑娘长得漂漂亮亮，怎么做事情笨手笨脚的", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289023}, {"id": 23080, "content": "软妹纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287513}, {"id": 22825, "content": "你好厉害，换我就做不到了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276079}, {"id": 23081, "content": "你是我父亲吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290377}, {"id": 22826, "content": "生下来就这么帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289042}, {"id": 22827, "content": "你特么真爷们儿！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281491}, {"id": 22828, "content": "啊~你是技师吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288993}, {"id": 23341, "content": "你的双眼皮在哪做的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205349}, {"id": 23854, "content": "你很帅了不起啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294076}, {"id": 22832, "content": "g h h", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289069}, {"id": 22834, "content": "约吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287133}, {"id": 23858, "content": "没有你我就死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294147}, {"id": 23861, "content": "我喜欢的人说：“你的声音很好听，我是一个声控对声音很挑剔”，虽然我们在一起的可能性接近于零，但是真的很高兴她的称赞，希望她能幸福。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104589}, {"id": 23862, "content": "没有你我就死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294147}, {"id": 22841, "content": "“长这么帅还要凭能力吃饭还让不让我们屌丝活啊。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162457}, {"id": 23097, "content": "浓缩就是精华啊...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290501}]}